  <section|Description>

  When insert a full-width punctuation via input method, on macOS and Windows, it failed with the following error message:

  <\scm-code>
    ;unbound variable keyboard-speech

    ; (== (get-input-mode) 1)

    ; (key-press key) \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ ; key: "speech:\<less\>#FF08\<gtr\>"

    ; ((with after? (in-inactive-reference?) (w... ; before?: #f
  </scm-code>

  <\scm-code>
    ;unbound variable keyboard-speech

    ; (== (get-input-mode) 1)

    ; (key-press key) \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ ; key: "speech:\\x10;"

    ; ((with after? (in-inactive-reference?) (w... ; before?: #f
  </scm-code>

